    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="main-container">
        <h1>Algorithm for Data Encryption Standard</h1>
        <p>This demo illustrates the DES encryption process. Enter a message and key, select the number of encryption rounds, and view the encrypted output in hexadecimal format for each even-numbered step up to the selected value.</p>

        <div id="control-panel">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="input-message">Message</label>
